'''Chags''' were small [[Hapes/Legends|Hapan]] amphibians, said to be highly excitable and unpredictable.

During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Atin Skirata|RC-3222]] compared the actions of the [[Null-class Advanced Recon Commando]]s to that of Hapan chags, and towards the beginning of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], [[Boba Fett/Legends|Boba Fett]] matched up politicians to a bucket of chags.

==Behind the scenes==
Author [[Karen Traviss]] created and defined chags for her short story ''[[Odds]]'', first published in [[Star Wars Insider 87|''Star Wars Insider'' #87]]. She later reused the creature for the [[eBook]] ''[[Boba Fett: A Practical Man]]''. However, chags have never actually appeared in the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars Legends|Expanded Universe]]; they are merely mentioned.

